reviews.reviewText: I got the 17 inch bag, I absolutely love it. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pretty and functional
reviews.reviewText: Bought this to use on a week-long business trip. Love the large floral print on the outside, and love how huge the bag itself is - I could fit my laptop, charger, mouse, notebook, light sweater, water bottle, phone, wallet, snack, etc. very easily. The “fabric” on the inside feels thin and plastic-y (not really like textile fabric, more like a low quality poncho type material?) but I’m the only one who sees/uses that so not a big deal to me as long as the pockets hold up well over time. And there are plenty of pockets and pen holder loops! The two handles are a great length on the longest setting, so it’s easy to get the bag up onto your shoulder with just one hand. I didn’t use the single detachable shoulder strap that came with it. Have only used the bag for the one trip thus far, so don’t have much feedback on durability yet, but it worked very well for my needs and I felt fabulous carrying it. :)
